source.name: Natural Gas Acquisition Program
source.description: The "NGAP" system is a web based application which serves NGAP GSA users for tracking information details for various natural gas supply chain elements like Agency, LDC, and Facility with their respective Point of Contacts information. In addition to this, it also maintains the Cost & Usage Data and Invoices for the Facilities under different account managers.
